Conch republic should produce the new smartphone. The payback period for the project at 2.7 is a lot less than the 7-year period after which the equipment bought for the project will have depreciated entirely. The net present value is above zero and the internal rate of return is greater than the required rate, which means that the returns from producing the new smartphone will outweigh the costs. Additionally, the profitability index is above 1, at 1.344, which means that for every dollar invested in producing the new smartphone, the company will benefit an additional $ 0.344.		

